description:
AJSM-26 EMBROIDERED CHIFFON 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Chiffon Trouser:  Silk Dupatta: Chiffon Color: Purple

Impress everyone with ‘The Noorie’ soft beauty look, graced by Minal Khan. Elevate your fashion game by draping this ethereal blush pink chiffon and poly cotton ensemble that is sure to double your style quotient. Adorned with lavish zariwork and delicate floral embroidery, this piece reflects the spirit of purity and simplicity, depicting aesthetical vibe. Paired this alluring hue of orchid so you can step out in finesse.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered Front Neckline On Chiffon
1.5 Meter Embroidered Front & Back With Border On Chiffon
Embroidered Sleeves With Border On Chiffon
3 Meter Embroidered Border For Chaak On Chiffon
2.5 Meter Embroidered Dupatta On Chiffon With 2 Side Borders
1.5 Meter Wide Width Silk For Trouser
